aott/analysis/escape_analysis/escape_detector.runa
Object Escape Detection Module for AOTT Memory Optimization

This module provides escape analysis for the Runa AOTT system including:
- Object allocation escape detection
- Method escape analysis
- Thread escape identification
- Global escape tracking
- Capture analysis for closures
- Reference escape paths
- Partial escape analysis
- Interprocedural escape flow
- Dynamic escape monitoring
- Escape state lattice computation
- Connection graph construction
- Field-sensitive escape tracking
- Array element escape analysis
- Escape through exceptions
- Speculative non-escape optimization
:End Note

Import "dev/debug/errors/core" as Errors

